  "keyFeatures": [
    "Pre-built agent packs for 18+ business types (solo founders, startups, agencies, local businesses)",
    "Coordinated multi-agent teams with an Orchestrator Agent that routes work and escalates when needed",
    "Bring-your-own LLM keys (Claude, Codex, Gemini) — no token markup",
    "Approval policies with dollar and action thresholds per agent",
    "Tool scopes granting per-agent, per-action access to connected tools",
    "Per-agent budgets and rate limits",
    "Full audit trail of every message, tool call, and approval",
    "SSO & SAML for enterprise workspaces",
    "Sandboxed, isolated agent execution with no ambient access",
    "Integrations with Notion, Slack, Gmail, Google Drive, HubSpot, GitHub, Linear, Stripe, and more"
